    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/627690/extras/24eb1cd8c66093fc6e8916db6667bf22.poster.avif?t=1771611129\" width=600 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/627690/extras/24eb1cd8c66093fc6e8916db6667bf22.webm?t=1771611129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/627690/extras/24eb1cd8c66093fc6e8916db6667bf22.mp4?t=1771611129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/627690/extras/a5b38316cf3818cf03bffcac16df901c.avif?t=1771611129\" width=600 height=108 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募传奇勇士，踏上无尽的终极冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Idle Champions of the Forgotten Realms》是一款策略管理游戏，将来自桌面角色扮演游戏战役、电子游戏、小说、实况游戏、漫画书和表演中的标志性勇士聚集在一起，展开一场宏大的冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用超过 140 名各具独特技能的勇士优化你的阵型，击败无数的怪物，完成数百次冒险。要精通这款游戏需要在每次冒险中不断推进阵型——只有最强大的阵型才能完成《Idle Champions》中最严峻的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/627690/extras/4d8682e29ae6a9c3518faca3cab0bd31.avif?t=1771611129\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集标志性勇士</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁来自整个《龙与地下城》宇宙的独特勇士，他们个个都有自己的阵型技能和杀招。粉丝们最爱的勇士包括崔斯特·杜垩登和秘银五侠、明斯克和布布、来自《博德之门 3》的阿斯代伦和卡菈克……以及很多很多其他勇士！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/627690/extras/bffe8ce1b3c37af63f7ad567471ed2b9.avif?t=1771611129\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>上手很容易，精通很难</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理多支探险队，测试你手下勇士的勇气，并获取更丰厚的奖励。即使你关闭了游戏，你的勇士也会自动与敌人战斗，直到被打败为止。你的魔宠会自动进行基本的游戏操作，例如升级勇士和拾取金币，这样你就可以专心优化你的阵型策略。构建强大的协同效果，释放你手下勇士的全部力量，完成最困难的冒险吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/627690/extras/5b2f1ed10000086846bff116ad1cf12a.avif?t=1771611129\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>漫游《龙与地下城》多元宇宙</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在剑湾和更遥远的地方展开冒险旅程。造访多座传奇名城，如博德之门、深水城和“众门之城”印记城。探索巴洛维亚的迷雾，于阿弗纳斯的无尽血战中冲杀，在星界之海中航行。<strong></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/627690/extras/2697815563d062147acea97909336432.avif?t=1771611129\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>定期内容更新</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每月会有多次内容更新。《Idle Champions》自 2017 年推出以来，已经引入了 140 多名勇士，推出了超过 200 个冒险，以及根据官方桌面角色扮演游戏内容制作的 8 个战役，并在游戏中增添了数十项新功能和系统。下一个重大更新永远不会让你等太久！</p>",
